ps://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;头皮总长一些红色小疙瘩，是咋回事？】头皮上长出像“痘痘”的红色小包，又疼又痒，这就是毛囊发炎的症状。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;医生介绍，不经常洗头、头发出油出汗等，金黄色葡萄球菌会疯狂生长，破坏头皮菌群平衡，引起红色丘疹和脓疱。另外，熬夜、吃油腻食物等，也会导致头皮皮肤屏障破坏或出油过多👇🏻&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（央视新闻）&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4832906183639072&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;央视新闻的微博视频&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br clear=&quot;both&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;clear: both&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;video controls=&quot;controls&quot; poster=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1h7voqkv0lsj61981oakjl02.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 100%&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/lv97z4Yglx080zJh3qR201041200nulC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;amp;template=720x1192.24.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1724547490&amp;amp;ssig=voDlOdXVvm&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/WlpF35qllx080zJgX38k01041200dYZ60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;amp;template=540x892.24.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=172